<body>
    <div class="progress" id="progress-bar" style="width: 0%;"></div>
    <div class="slide-counter" id="counter" onclick="promptSlide()" title="Click to jump to a slide">Loading...</div>

    <button class="side-nav left-nav" id="prevBtn" onclick="moveSlide(-1)" aria-label="Previous Slide">&#10094;</button>
    <button class="side-nav right-nav" id="nextBtn" onclick="moveSlide(1)" aria-label="Next Slide">&#10095;</button>

    <div class="slider" id="slider">
<div class="slide"><div class="content-box">
                <h1 style="text-align:center;">Class 10 Science</h1>
                <h2 style="border:none; margin-bottom: 0; text-align:center;">NCERT 150-Slide Masterpiece</h2>
                <p class="punjabi" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 5px; text-align:center;">(ਅਧਿਆਇ 1-5)</p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.6rem; color: #555; margin-top: 30px; text-align:center;">
                    <span class="accent-blue">Understand first.</span> <span class="punjabi">(ਪਹਿਲਾਂ ਸਮਝੋ)</span><br>
                    <span class="accent">Memorize second.</span> <span class="punjabi">(ਫਿਰ ਯਾਦ ਕਰੋ)</span><br>
                    Practice daily. <span class="punjabi">(ਰੋਜ਼ ਅਭਿਆਸ ਕਰੋ)</span>
                </p>
</div></div>
<div class="slide"><div class="content-box">
                <h2>PSEB Board Exam Tips <span class="punjabi">(ਬੋਰਡ ਪ੍ਰੀਖਿਆ ਲਈ ਸੁਝਾਅ)</span></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Write in Points:</strong> Break long paragraphs into short bullet points. Examiners prefer this!</li>
                    <li><strong>Draw Diagrams:</strong> Use pencil for diagrams (e.g., Micelle formation, Electrolytic refining). Label them clearly.</li>
                    <li><strong>Chemical Equations:</strong> Always write <em>balanced</em> equations and mention physical states (s, l, g, aq).</li>
                    <li><strong>Read "Give Reasons" carefully:</strong> Be specific. Example: "Why does curd turn sour in copper?" &rarr; Mention "Reaction with metal to form toxic salts."</li>
                </ul>
</div></div>
<div class="slide"><div class="content-box">
                <h2>How to Learn Science <span class="punjabi">(ਵਿਗਿਆਨ ਕਿਵੇਂ ਸਿੱਖੀਏ)</span></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Read slowly. <span class="punjabi">(ਹੌਲੀ ਪੜ੍ਹੋ)</span></li>
                    <li>Learn the key word. <span class="punjabi">(ਮੁੱਖ ਸ਼ਬਦ ਸਿੱਖੋ)</span></li>
                    <li>Look at one example. <span class="punjabi">(ਉਦਾਹਰਣ ਦੇਖੋ)</span></li>
                    <li>Say the idea out loud. <span class="punjabi">(ਉੱਚੀ ਆਵਾਜ਼ ਵਿੱਚ ਬੋਲੋ)</span></li>
                    <li>Practice with Short Answers. <span class="punjabi">(ਛੋਟੇ ਉੱਤਰਾਂ ਦਾ ਅਭਿਆਸ ਕਰੋ)</span></li>
                    <li>Write equations by hand. <span class="punjabi">(ਸਮੀਕਰਣਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਲਿਖੋ)</span></li>
