                <h2>Reaction Prediction Flowchart <span class="punjabi">(ਕਿਰਿਆ ਦੀ ਭਵਿੱਖਬਾਣੀ)</span></h2>
                <p>Don't just memorize! Ask yourself these questions to find the reaction type:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Are two elements combining into one? &rarr; <strong>Combination</strong></li>
                    <li>Is there only ONE reactant being heated? &rarr; <strong>Decomposition</strong></li>
                    <li>Is it a single element reacting with a compound? &rarr; <strong>Displacement</strong></li>
                    <li>Are two compounds exchanging ions? &rarr; <strong>Double Displacement</strong></li>
                </ul>
