ss="punjabi">(ਕਾਰਬਨ ਦਾ ਬਹੁਮੁਖੀ ਸੁਭਾਅ)</span></h2>
                <p>Why are there millions of carbon compounds?</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Catenation <span class="punjabi">(ਲੜੀਬੰਧਨ)</span>:</strong> Carbon has the unique ability to form long chains, branched chains, and rings by bonding with other carbon atoms.</li>
                    <li><strong>Tetravalency <span class="punjabi">(ਚੌ-ਸੰਜੋਜਕਤਾ)</span>:</strong> Because it has 4 valence electrons, carbon can bond with 4 other atoms (like H, O, N, S, or Cl) simultaneously.</li>
