 data-correct="true" onclick="checkAnswer(this, true, true)">B. Silicon</button><button class="option-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this, false, true)">C. Sulphur</button><div class="feedback"></div><button class="next-sub-btn" onclick="nextSubSlide('mcq-ch5', 10)">Next Question &rarr;</button></div><div class="sub-slide" id="mcq-ch5-s10"><div class="sub-progress">Question 10 of 12</div><div class="question-text">How many periods are there in the Modern Periodic Table?<br><span class="punjabi-block">ਆਧੁਨਿਕ ਆਵਰਤੀ ਸਾਰਣੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਕਿੰਨੇ ਪੀਰੀਅਡ ਹਨ?</span></div><button class="option-btn" data-correct="true" onclick="checkAnswer(this, true, true)">A. 7</button><button class="option-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this, false, true)">B. 8</button><button class="option-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this, false, true)">C. 18</button><div class="feedback"></div><button class="next-sub-btn" onclick="nextSubSlide('mcq-ch5', 11)">Next Question &rarr;</button></div><div class="sub-slide" id="mcq-ch5-s11"><div class="sub-progress">Question 11 of 12</div><div class="question-text">The isotopes of an element have the same:<br><span class="punjabi-block">ਇੱਕ ਤੱਤ ਦੇ ਸਮਸਥਾਨਕਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੀ ਸਮਾਨ ਹੁੰਦਾ ਹੈ?</span></div><button class="option-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this, false, true)">A. Atomic mass</button><button class="option-btn" data-correct="true" onclick="checkAnswer(this, true, true)">B. Atomic number</button><button class="option-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this, false, true)">C. Number of neutrons</button><div class="feedback"></div><button class="next-sub-btn" onclick="nextSubSlide('mcq-ch5', 12)">Next Question &rarr;</button></div><div class="sub-slide" id="mcq-ch5-s12"><div class="sub-progress">Question 12 of 12</div><div class="question-text">Modern periodic law relates physical and chemical properties to:<br><span class="punjabi-block">ਆਧੁਨਿਕ ਆਵਰਤੀ ਨਿਯਮ ਭੌਤਿਕ ਅਤੇ ਰਸਾਇਣਕ ਗੁਣਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਕਿਸ ਨਾਲ ਜੋੜਦਾ ਹੈ?</span></div><button class="option-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this, false, true)">A. Atomic masses</butt